### Key Methodology Notes

- Analysis based on data as of August 2021
- Compares 11 major countries across multiple dimensions
- Uses Z-scores to standardize measurements across different metrics
- Trajectory indicators: ⬆ (getting better), ⬇ (getting worse), ➜ (flat)
- **Big cycles** interact with and reinforce **measures of power** to move countries along their cycle
